<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe8d3859-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s8278"><num value="8278">§ 8278.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purposes of this part, there is authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary not to exceed $98,000,000 for the period beginning <date date="1978-10-01">October 1, 1978</date>, and ending <date date="1981-09-30">September 30, 1981</date>.</p>
